parameter.string: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <?eclipse version="3.0"?> <plugin> <extension point="org.eclipse.graphiti.ui.diagramTypes"> <diagramType description="This is the generated diagram Type for $context.graphModelName$" id="$context.packageName$.$context.graphModelName$DiagramType" name="$context.graphModelName$ Graphiti Diagram Type" type="$context.graphModelName$"> </diagramType> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.graphiti.ui.diagramTypeProviders"> <diagramTypeProvider class="$context.packageName$.graphiti.$context.graphModelName$DiagramTypeProvider" description="This is the generated editor for the $context.graphModelName$" id="$context.packageName$.$context.graphModelName$DiagramTypeProvider" name="$context.graphModelName$ Diagram Editor"> <diagramType id="$context.packageName$.$context.graphModelName$DiagramType"> </diagramType> <imageProvider id="$context.packageName$.$context.graphModelName$ImageProvider"> </imageProvider> </diagramTypeProvider> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.graphiti.ui.imageProviders"> <imageProvider class="$context.packageName$.graphiti.$context.graphModelName$ImageProvider" id="$context.packageName$.$context.graphModelName$ImageProvider"> </imageProvider> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.ui.views.properties.tabbed.propertyContributor"> <propertyContributor contributorId="$context.graphModelName$.PropertyContributor"> <propertyCategory category="$context.graphModelName$"></propertyCategory> </propertyContributor> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.ui.views.properties.tabbed.propertyTabs"> <propertyTabs contributorId="$context.graphModelName$.PropertyContributor"> <propertyTab category="$context.graphModelName$" id="$context.packageName$.graphiti.property.$context.graphModelName$PropertyTab" label="Base"> </propertyTab> </propertyTabs> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.ui.views.properties.tabbed.propertySections"> <propertySections contributorId="$context.graphModelName$.PropertyContributor"> $context.propertySectionCode$ </propertySections> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.ui.newWizards"> <wizard class="$context.projectName$.wizard.New$context.fuGraphModelName$DiagramWizard" $context.iconPathContent$ id="$context.projectName$.wizard.$context.lcGraphModelName$" name="New $context.fuGraphModelName$"> </wizard> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.ui.editors"> <editor class="$context.projectName$.$context.fuGraphModelName$DiagramEditor" contributorClass="org.eclipse.graphiti.ui.editor.DiagramEditorActionBarContributor" default="false" $context.iconPathContent$ id="$context.projectName$.$context.fuGraphModelName$Editor" matchingStrategy="org.eclipse.graphiti.ui.editor.DiagramEditorMatchingStrategy" name="$context.graphModelName$ Editor"> <contentTypeBinding contentTypeId="$context.projectName$.$context.fuGraphModelName$ContentType"> </contentTypeBinding> <contentTypeBinding contentTypeId="org.eclipse.graphiti.content.diagram"> </contentTypeBinding> </editor> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.core.contenttype.contentTypes"> <content-type file-extensions="$context.extension$" id="$context.projectName$.$context.fuGraphModelName$ContentType" name="$context.fuGraphModelName$ Content Type" priority="normal"> </content-type> </extension> <extension point="org.eclipse.ui.popupMenus"> <objectContribution adaptable="false" id="$context.projectName$.$context.graphModelName$ObjectContributor" nameFilter="*$context.extension$" objectClass="org.eclipse.core.resources.IResource"> <action class="$context.projectName$.Create$context.graphModelName$Diagram" id="$context.projectName$.Create$context.graphModelName$DiagramAction" label="Create $context.graphModelName$ Diagram"> </action> </objectContribution> </extension> </plugin>
